---
title: Roasted Chickpea Salad with Honey-Tahini Drizzle and Stovetop Croutons
description: This colourful, Middle Eastern-inspired salad delights with complementary textures and balanced flavours. A mix of fresh veggies and greens is topped with croutons, roasted chickpeas and a creamy tahini drizzle!
